{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/district-valuer-services-dvs/about/complaints-procedure","content_id":"6020ef3c-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","description":"How to make a complaint about District Valuer Services (DVS).","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>In the first place, contact us to set out your complaint and we will let you know the action we can take, or explain why we can’t take action.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact contact\" id=\"contact_2258\">\n    <p class=\"govuk-body\">Enquiries</p>\n\n\n    <div>\n        <p class=\"govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-4\">\n          Email <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"mailto:clientdevelopment@voa.gov.uk\">clientdevelopment@voa.gov.uk</a>\n        </p>\n\n\n    </div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n<p>If you are not satisfied with our response and wish to make a formal complaint, follow the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/valuation-office-agency/about/complaints-procedure\" class=\"govuk-link\">Valuation Office Agency’s procedure</a>.</p>\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2014-12-01T12:40:14Z"}],"organisation":"32cc780c-3902-4ad6-b13d-17b445f11693","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"complaints_procedure","first_published_at":"2014-12-01T12:40:14+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/district-valuer-services-dvs/about/complaints-procedure","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/district-valuer-services-dvs/about/complaints-procedure","base_path":"/government/organisations/district-valuer-services-dvs/about/complaints-procedure","content_id":"6020ef3c-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","document_type":"complaints_procedure","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-12-01T12:40:14Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"Complaints procedure","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/district-value